I've got your ticket pulled up and it looks like the only response you've gotten so far was from the automated Blitzbot which was letting you know that we can't verify your information while signed into your account. 

In order to start the account recovery process, you'll need to submit a new ticket in the [**account recovery form**](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/requests/new?ticket_form_id=72416) and remember to **stay signed out when you submit that ticket**.
